PIT|Reading iMessage conversation history
PIT|Checking recent Messages.app chats
PIT|Sending to phone numbers or Apple IDs
PIT|Telegram/Discord/Slack/WhatsApp messages → use the appropriate gateway channel
PIT|Group chat management (adding/removing members) → not supported
PIT|Bulk/mass messaging → always confirm with user first
